data.title: Girona Railway Station Live Webcam
data.meta_description: Live cam locates in Girona, Catalonia, Spain. Girona Railway Station Webcam - enjoy watching online!
data.text: This live rail webcam stream displays a stretch of the railroad and station in downtown Girona, Spain. You will see many trains passing through from Barcelona–Cerbère conventional rail line and the Perpignan–Barcelona high-speed rail line. The online HD stream is brought to you by the Association of Friends of Girona Counties Railway.
